- FSP (Food Safety Platform)&#xd;
- EATIP (European Aquaculture Technology &amp; Innovation Platform)&#xd;
- EUFETEC (Platform composed of several feed-related bodies representing the feed industry and research institutes)&#xd;
- EPRUMA (European Platform for the Responsible Use of Medicines in Animals)  &#xd;
- FFC (EU feed &amp; food chain platform on biotechnology)&#xd;
- EU Feed Chain Task Force on the Catalogue of Feed Materials&#xd;
- Agri Food Chain Coalition on Innovation&#xd;
